## Rules
1. CSS import FIRST — always
2. DB HeaventRounded for ALL text — never Inter
3. Min font 14px — never smaller
4. Max 1 primary button per view
5. Always handle: loading (Skeleton), empty (EmptyState), error (Alert)
6. No heavy shadows — flat design only
7. No random colors — palette only

